                "institute": "2FR SAC"
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Reactor Pile EL.2. This beam also gave",
                " the neutrons for the creation of the fission neutron",
                " spectrum, and also the Maxwellian neutron spectrum."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                ".500 mg natural uranium in 40 deposits of 1.8 mg/cm2,",
                " produced by painting of uranyl nitrate onto",
                " the two sides of an Al foil of 0.03 mm thickness.",
                " There is  also a measurement done with a sample",
                " made poorer in U-235 (2.E-4 U235) in order to show",
                " that at 14.2 MeV the fissions come only from U-238",
                " in both of the samples."
              ]
            }
